:: TheKind.Session2.Position2_Hub
~ session.discussed_cards.append(cards[1].name)
@render render_reading(reading=reading, highlight=1)

You touch the second card.

**Position 2: What's Actually In The Way**
**{cards[1].name}**{cards[1].reversed ?  (Reversed) | }

The store is paying attention. You can feel it — the particular quality of a building that holds more than it should, leaning in, the aisles narrowing slightly the way they do when something important is happening in the reading nook. Through the bead curtain, you can see the deeper shelves — the ones that don't quite align with the architecture, the ones where Mal's composition notebook entries start to describe books that haven't been published yet — and they seem closer tonight. Interested.

